description:
Angel Fuentes is a self-published comic book writer from Puerto Rico. He founded and served as Publisher of RBA Comics, a studio composed of various artists and writers with the purpose of producing creator owned comics. Angel has created several comic titles such as Santa Cristal (2005), RBA Presents (2008-2010); Gunbreed (2008); You Complete Me (2009); Leviathans (2009); Violet Descends (2010); and Tainted (2010). He also edited the comic Kyu Shin (2009) written by Mitch Hyman for Scare Tactix Graphix.

In 2005, Angel wrote the screenplay and co-produced the Spanish independent film Santa Cristal. He also researched and wrote the script on the history of Puerto Rican comics for the documentary TV show Prohibido Olvidar (2010). Angel has a Masters Degree in Screenwriting. He recently relocated to New York and is currently writing a novelization of his comic Violet Descends.
name: Angel Fuentes
